17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 62 O.S. 2021, Section 34.301, as
18 last amended by Section 1, Chapter 134, O.S.L. 2023 (62 O.S. Supp.
19 2024, Section 34.301), is amended to read as follows:
20 Section 34.301. A. This act shall be known and may be cited as
21 the "Civil Service and Human Capital Modernization Act".
22 B. The Human Capital Management Division and the Civil Service
23 Division of the Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall:
